'''外星爬蟲人'''（{{lang-en|Reptilians}}，也稱為{{lang|en|Reptilian humanoids}}<ref>{{cite web|title=Fact or fiction? Tribune sets out to debunk 10 rural legends|url=http://www.greatfallstribune.com/article/20101226/LIFESTYLE/12260305/Fact-or-fiction-Tribune-sets-out-to-debunk-10-rural-legends|accessdate=2011-01-04|author=Kristen Inbody|date=2010-12-26|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101228081058/http://www.greatfallstribune.com/article/20101226/LIFESTYLE/12260305/Fact-or-fiction-Tribune-sets-out-to-debunk-10-rural-legends|archivedate=2010-12-28}}</ref>、{{lang|en|Reptoids}}<ref name="book, synonym ">{{cite web|title=Weiser Field Guide to the Paranormal, The: Abductions, Apparitions, ESP|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=9aYqjnjDzBQC&pg=PA80&dq=Reptilians+"also+known+as"&hl=en&ei=9PMiTY_pIYTJnAf134inDg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=4&ved=0CDEQ6|publisher=Weiser|author=Judith Joyce|year=2010|accessdate=2011-01-02}}</ref>、{{lang|en|Reptiloids}}或{{lang|en|Draconians}}），亦作'''爬蟲人'''或'''蜥蜴人'''，是目擊事件中出現的[[外星人|外星人]]之一。

外星爬蟲人時常與[[外星人誘拐|外星人誘拐]]事件還有[[陰謀論|陰謀論]]相提並論。這些爬蟲人的外表有淺綠色的麟片覆蓋，有琥珀色的眼睛<ref name=drama>{{Cite web |url=http://www.staradio.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Broadcast-Drama-Final.mp3 |title=The Weiser Field Guide to the Paranormal: Abductions, Apparitions, ESP |access-date=2013-07-12 |archive-date=2014-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140701191814/http://staradio.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Broadcast-Drama-Final.mp3 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 手指尖長，牙齒尖，五至六米<ref name=drama />或15呎高<ref name=thegreaterpicture>{{cite web |url=http://thegreaterpicture.com/reptilians.html |title=The Greater Picture - Reptilians |language=en |accessdate=2013-07-11 |archive-date=2013-06-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130625212027/http://thegreaterpicture.com/reptilians.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，懂得[[心靈感應|心靈感應]]。傳統上相信牠們能夠變形，有食用人類或吸飲人血的習慣，以保持人類的外型。陰謀論者還相信現時世界有不少政要其實也是牠們的同類變形而成的。2013年4月2日，根據一家專門分析政治動向的美國機構 — [[公共政策民調基金會|公共政策民調基金會]]所做的調查顯示，有4%的美國民眾投票認為，外星[[爬蟲|爬蟲]]人透過奪取[[政治|政治]][[權力|權力]]來控制人類社會<ref>{{cite web|language=en|url=http://www.publicpolicypolling.com/main/2013/04/conspiracy-theory-poll-results-.html|title=Conspiracy Theory Poll Results|publisher=[[公共政策民調基金會|公共政策民調基金會]]|date=2013-04-02|accessdate=2017-04-03|archive-date=2017-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170330202136/http://www.publicpolicypolling.com/main/2013/04/conspiracy-theory-poll-results-.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

